restybuddy project

restybuddy project is a project focus on backend.

we are want to build an intelligent backend with good performance.

so , that's go!

we use :

openresty, is a good performance of nginx , it include so many modules with nginx. recommend.
php, is many useful of web application development.
lua, is a tiny program language.
yaf, is a good performance and so lightly php framework.
redis, is a good famous nosql database.
sphinx, is a good performance search solution.

how to do:
0.download openresty from http://openresty.org ,then install it,second download php,then install it.
1.install git ,then clone our project code.
3.start nginx with our configs.
4.browe this url from webbrowser. if u see "hello world" , then u success.






